item.description:
This month's meeting will be off by 1 week due to scheduling conflicts, but if you think of it as a "Spring Ahead" change it kind of works. We're just Springing Ahead one week. Karen Macedo, faculty at MCC will be presenting on Illustrator. She will be giving an overview of Illustrator, comparing how some things are familiar to a Photoshop user, and somethings that are different as well as some of the cool things you can do with AI.  If you have anything to share, we welcome that as well. We hope to see you all on Thursday night, 3/22/2012 at 6:00pm!!

 

We shall be meeting in room HSCI 107 tonight.
item.name: March Manchester Adobe User Group Meeting
